Subject: Re: [T2] Fuel Line Size

> Can someone tell me the fuel line size for the hose between the fuel filter
> and fuel pump on a 1975 fuel injected bus?

It is 10mm.
It is available at your local Mercedes Benz dealer. A while back I posted the
MB part # for it. It is 112 476 12 26. Suggested list then was $15.50 a meter
[39 1/4''] but you only need about 4''.
